paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the structural analysis of ATTRwt amyloid fibrils in the TTR gene using cryo-EM, focusing on structural homogeneity and its potential link to clinical presentation. No specific genetic variants in the TTR gene are mentioned.

challenges: The paper did not mention specific genetic variants in the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on structural analysis of amyloid fibrils in ATTRwt amyloidosis without detailing specific genetic variants.
